Release Notes - Early Detection of Cancer - Version eCAS Browser beta 0.5.1 release - 08/29/2011


** Bug
    * [CA-769] - Cannot download files - 403 - page does not exist error.
    * [CA-773] - Label mismatch on ecas browser homepage due to changed defaults
    * [CA-774] - Link to the public portal from the ecas home page
    * [CA-777] - not all protocols showing up on ecas browser "protocol" filter
    * [CA-790] - http 500 error returned from 'collab group' filters (all except lung) on ecas home page

** Improvement
    * [CA-757] - Need to change RDF dataset URL format for eCAS datasets to match new 0.5.0 beta browser
    * [CA-776] - Add protocol name to the dataset "teaser" shown on the ecas home page



